SUMMARY:Angry At Numbers\, The Rockford Mules\, Whiskey Rock n Roll Club\, Modern Dads
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook and Ladder Theater \n\nDoors 7:30pm :: Music 8:00pm \n\n21+ \n\nGA: $15 Advance  / $20  Day of Show\n\n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nAngry At Numbers\, The Rockford Mules\, Whiskey Rock n Roll Club\, & Modern Dads\n\n—–\n \n\nLive Music For The Day of The Dead!The Hook & Ladder is excited to present this guitar driven 4-band Rock & Roll bill in our cozy Mission Room\, featuring sets by; Angry At Numbers\, The Rockford Mules\, Whiskey Rock n Roll Club and Modern Dads! \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/angry-mules-rock-dads/
LOCATION:Hook and Ladder Mission Room\, 3010 Minnehaha\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Mission Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/image-40.jpeg
END:VEVENT
