SUMMARY:Hell or High Water - Hurricane Relief Show
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook AND LADDER THEATER \n\nDoors 5:00pm :: Music 5:30pm \n\n18+\n\nGA: $10 ADV / $15 DOS\n\n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nHell or High Water – Hurricane Relief Show\nw/ Ghosting Merit\, Watches\, Doll Chaser\, Fend\, BlueDriver  \n———- \nA benefit show for relief and rebuilding efforts for Western NC communities impacted by recent catastrophic storms. Proceeds go to Pansy Collective\, a trans-aid group based out of Appalachia that for the foreseeable future has diverted all effort and funds into hurricane relief.\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/hellorhighwater/
LOCATION:The Hook and Ladder Theater\, 3010 Minnehaha Ave\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Fundraiser,Hook & Ladder Theater
