SUMMARY:The Get Together\, Samantha Grimes\, Nicholas David & Demitrious Rallis
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe MISSION ROOM AT THE HOOK \n\nDoors 7:00pm\nMusic 7:30pm\n21+ \nGeneral Admission: $12 Advance / $18 Day of Show\n\n*Does not include feesNO REFUNDS \n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Get Together\, Samantha Grimes\,\nNicholas David & Demitrious Rallis\n—-Want a one of a kind show!? Join us at the Hook and Ladder Mission Room for just that! This lineup is sure to dazzle you with incredible music. Kick back and relax to the Get together and their indie groove\, Or Samantha Grimes witty lyrics and strong vocals\, last but not least Greg Hall and the Wrecking Ball to push the envelope on boot stomping and captivating performances. This is truly a night for all music lovers! \n— \nNeo-psychedelic/Indie Rock \nThe Get Together began with the writings and recordings of producer Ethan Huffington. Surrounded by his plants and pedals in a wood panelled Minneapolis basement\, he set about crafting neo-psychedelic journeys through otherworldly dreamscapes. A get together necessarily involves more than one person however\, and via the serendipitous magic of the internet a band soon coalesced around his songs. Together\, they created a live act that showcases their combined creative energies\, while reinterpreting and expanding upon the recorded discography \n— \nSamantha Grimes Folk\, rock\, blues\, country and more combine to create the iconic sound of Americana grown in the Midwest. With hits like “Wendy Darling\,” “Wicked Mortals” and “Trainwreck\,” Samantha Grimes has shown her ability to captivate listeners in all genres. \n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/together-grime-hall/
LOCATION:Hook and Ladder Mission Room\, 3010 Minnehaha\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Live Music,Mission Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/THE-GET-TOGETHER-2160-x-1080-px.png
END:VEVENT
