SUMMARY:Elder Voice Advocates Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook and Ladder Theater \n\n6pm Cocktail Hour :: 7pm Music :: 21+ \nGeneral Admission: $20 ADV / $25 DOS\n\n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nElder Voice Advocates Fundraiser\n\nThe Hook & Ladder Theater is proud to partner with Elder Voice Advocates on their exciting inaugural live fundraiser event\, featuring music by Glycerin Tears\, raffles/prizes\, food trucks\, cash-bar and much more! \n \n\nElder Voice Advocates is a Minnesota non-profit that advocates for quality care for elders and adults with disabilities. Born out of devastating experiences by members’ loved ones in long term care settings\, their volunteer driven organization has strengthened and changed laws through education and advocacy for over 60\,000 Minnesotans. \n\nJoin us in listening to the fabulous 70’s band “Glycerin Tears” \, performing the best rock tunes recorded between 1970 and 1979! \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/eldervoiceadvocates-fundraiser/
LOCATION:The Hook and Ladder Theater\, 3010 Minnehaha Ave\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Fundraiser,Hook & Ladder Theater
