SUMMARY:Trent Romans Band\, JoJo Green\, Clay Fulton & The Lost Forty
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe MISSION ROOM AT THE HOOK \n\nDoors 7:00pm\nMusic 7:30pm\n21+ \nGeneral Admission: $12 Advance / $18 Day of Show\n\n*Does not include feesNO REFUNDS \n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nTrent Romans Band\, JoJo Green\, Clay Fulton & The Lost Forty\n—- \nGet ready for a night intertwined with blues and fusion. This three band lineup promises to bring high energy along with a soulful night\, in the one of a kind Mission Room at the Hook And Ladder. \n— \nTrent Romens Band is a Blues-Soul-Jam band hailing from the Twin Cities. Fronted by longtime local blues guitarist Trent Romens\, this band is a culmination of Trent’s ability to write songs and captivate an audience.—JoJo Green features rich\, agile\, and daring trios between their bodacious vocalist\, diva\, and band leader\, Sharisse Germain\, cheeky and fearless saxophonist\, Zach Miller\, and smooth\, suave guitarist\, Conner Allen\, braiding through each performance. The JoJo groove is driven by primal\, soulful rhythm provided by drummer Nancy Long and bassist/lead songwriter Scott Yonke \n— \nClay Fulton and the Lost FortyRoots Rock/Country \nClay Fulton is a singer-songwriter from Rochester\, Minnesota. His debut album When Trouble Comes has been a long time coming. Songs like “Walls Of St. Paul” and “When Trouble Comes” were written while studying at McNally Smith College of Music in St. Paul\, Minnesota. \n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/romens-jojo-lost/
LOCATION:Hook and Ladder Mission Room\, 3010 Minnehaha\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Live Stream,Mission Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/TRomens-JGreen-CFulton_1122-hookmission2160x1080.png
