SUMMARY:Gently\, Gently with Crush Scene & KYM and the Kick
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe MISSION ROOM AT THE HOOK \n\nDoors 7:00pm\nMusic 7:30pm\n21+ \nGeneral Admission: $12 Advance / $18 Day of Show\n\n*Does not include feesNO REFUNDS \n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\nGently\, Gently\nwith Crush Scene\, KYM and the Kick \n— \nGet ready for a night intertwined with blues\, funk\, rock\, punk\, pop and femme Ya’llternative Barbie rock! \nGently\, Gently\nMinneapolis Rock Group Gently\, Gently creates and performs original songs that blend an array of genres including blues\, funk\, country\, and punk rock. Their gripping lyrics dive head-first into the themes and effects of sudden change\, self-discovery\, and what it means to look vastly different from the person you thought you would grow into. Join them for sensual melodies\, heartfelt emotions\, urgent rhythms\, and honest words meant to evoke the listener’s own sense of self. \nCrush Scene\nCrush Scene is a 4 piece femme Ya’llternative Barbie rock band. \nKYM and the Kick\nKYM and the Kick is a cheeky pop trio out of the Twin Cities\, Minnesota. If you like Chappell Roan\, Alanis Morissette\, Jade Bird…. you found the right place honey.KYM and the Kick released their EP\, “Not 4 U\,” under their solo name KYM in 2020 — six pop tracks with a hint of early 2000s rock. “Not 4 U” is the EP you reach for when your day was crap\, and you need to dance it out in your underwear in front of the mirror. They released their first single under the new band name in September 2024. “Soft on You” is an ode to the softness of love\, and the bravery it takes to open up. KYM and the Kick’s debut album\, “The Gift of Feeling\,” comes out in February 2025. \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/gentlygently-crushscene-kym-kick/
LOCATION:Hook and Ladder Mission Room\, 3010 Minnehaha\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Mission Room
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/241123-Mission-GentlyGently-2160x1080-Eventbrite.jpg
