DESCRIPTION:RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n EVENT DETAILS \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook and Ladder Theater \n\nDoors 8pm:: Music 8:30pm\n21+\n$10 Advance / $15 Day of Show\n\n  \n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\nBasement Apartment\, Denim Matriarch\, & Muun Bato\n\nThe Hook & Ladder Theater Presents: A night of Psych & Prog Rock straight outta Death Valley Junction. \nThree exciting bands; Basement Apartment\, Denim Matriarch\, & Muun Bato \n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
