SUMMARY:Light 'em The Bong Show 2.0
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook AND LADDER THEATER \n\n7pm Doors (Social Smoke Hour) :: 8pm Show :: 21+\nGA: $15 ADV / $20 DOS\n\n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nRetro Bakery presents\nLight ’em Up The BONG SHOW 2.0\n“20th Anniversary Tour”\nThe Hook hosts a unique and interactive comedy improv experience for Twin City comedy and cannabis fans!\n \nThe Hook is teaming up with local comic/host/producer Ira Ford\, our friends at Retro Bakery\, Zen Arcade\, Green Piece Minnesota and twelve very special Midwest comedians to present a live stand-up showcase/competition – Light ‘em Up\, The Bong Show!\n \n\nThis ‘highbred’ comedy event embraces MN cannabis culture by purposely blurring the lines between audience members and performers with an open pre-show smoke-out on the Twin Cities largest cannabis friendly patio at The Hook.  \nTwelve (12) ‘contender’ comics will compete telling prewritten and improvisational material.  Audience members will hold their lit phones up to judge the winners of each round. Join us in person to see how it all unfolds.\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/bongshow-2/
LOCATION:The Hook and Ladder Theater\, 3010 Minnehaha Ave\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Comedy,Hook & Ladder Theater
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/image-3.png
