SUMMARY:Drinksgiving with ELnO + DJ TimeMachine
DESCRIPTION:EVENT DETAILS \n\n    RSVP ON FACEBOOK\n  \n\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nThe Hook AND LADDER THEATER \n\n\nDoors 7:00pm :: Music 7:30pm :: 21+\n\nReserved Seats (Limited): $40\nGeneral Admission*: $25 ADV / $32 DOS\nTickets On-Sale 11/1 @10am\n\n\n    COVID-19 Policies\n  \n\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n EVENT DESCRIPTION \n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\nDrinksgiving with ELnO + DJ TimeMachine\nELnO Drinksgiving is that beloved annual tradition that takes place the night before “that other” beloved annual tradition. This year\, thanks to the magic of 23 & Me and the telephone line\, we’ve reconnected with long-lost Jeff Lynnes from all over the world. Don’t miss your chance to see the biggest round-up ever assembled on one stage. More Lynnes than you can shake a drumstick at! Count on maximum talent and mega wigs. And get ready to dance like no one is watching to the super 70’s sounds of DJ TimeMachine. Join us as we gather at the Hook & Ladder Theater to give thanks for a Jeff Lynne bounty beyond compare. One night only! \n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n\n	\n		\n\n	\n	\n\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\n	\n								\n									\n					\n								\n\n	\n	\n		\n					\n\n	\n\n	\n				\n			\n			\nThis activity is made possible by the voters of Minnesota through a Minnesota State Arts Board Operating Support grant\, thanks to a legislative appropriation from the arts and cultural heritage fund.
URL:https://thehookmpls.com/event/24-drinksgiving/
LOCATION:The Hook and Ladder Theater\, 3010 Minnehaha Ave\, Minneapolis\, MN\, 55406\, United States
CATEGORIES:Concerts,Hook & Ladder Theater
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://thehookmpls.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/DRINKSGIVING-24-BANNER-.jpg
